data.description: Prime location right in the middle between Channel Lake, Lake Catherine, and Lake Marie on the Chain of Lakes. Cozy cottage on a double lot, updated throughout in 2017 with new windows, new pergo flooring, newer kitchen cabinets, newer appliances, washer and dryer, newer bathroom with a shower,  HVAC is older but in a great working condition. Freshly painted, new closet doors. Large living room and kitchen with great yard space for summer gatherings after a day on the water! Side deck and concrete poured and ready for a 2 car garage to be built.    2 Pin #'s 01-12-305-007 & 01-12-305-008.
